by your nagging.

16:53.388 --> 16:54.973
- Oh, my God.
- Don't worry, guys.

16:54.973 --> 16:56.391
Okay, I'm gonna get it.

16:56.391 --> 16:57.934
Okay, s-sometimes
it helps if you're angry.

16:57.934 --> 16:59.436
You...you can channel that
into your finger,

16:59.436 --> 17:00.979
like when you punch a wall.

17:00.979 --> 17:03.940
- [grunts]
- Come on, sweetie, you got it.

17:03.940 --> 17:05.567
- Come on!
- [grunts]

17:05.567 --> 17:09.446
That's it. That's right.
Come on, push it!

17:09.446 --> 17:11.406
[grunts]

17:11.406 --> 17:13.950
I can't get it, I'm sorry.
I think I hurt my finger too.

17:13.950 --> 17:15.285
- It's all right.
- All right, all right.

17:15.285 --> 17:16.494
