17:18.288 --> 17:21.291
[breathing deeply]

17:24.502 --> 17:26.254
- [exhales]
- Whoa!

17:26.254 --> 17:28.631
- Amazing!
- Oh, my gosh!

17:28.631 --> 17:30.717
