Oh, shit!

18:02.916 --> 18:04.626
- Great, honey!
- Oh, my God!

18:04.626 --> 18:06.294
That was pretty good.

18:06.294 --> 18:09.214
What are you...
what are you so angry about?

18:09.214 --> 18:11.424
Nothing.

18:11.424 --> 18:13.426
Okay.

18:13.426 --> 18:15.512
[man] See, honey, it's not
doing it anymore.

18:15.512 --> 18:19.098
I saw it, I swear.
The light was going crazy.

18:19.098 --> 18:21.059
- It was super creepy.
