20:07.290 --> 20:09.584
Again, I don't even know
if it's possible.

20:09.584 --> 20:14.005
I believe in you.
If anyone can do it, it's you.

20:14.005 --> 20:16.424
Well, you're right about that.

20:16.424 --> 20:18.885
Let me go inside,
get prepared.

20:18.885 --> 20:21.638
Try and scare the shit
out of these...

20:21.638 --> 20:22.931
