some thinking, and...

20:37.278 --> 20:41.282
I think maybe
we should let this go.

20:41.282 --> 20:43.201
- What do you mean?
- I mean, look.

20:43.201 --> 20:46.287
I...I think that we've
had great times here,

20:46.287 --> 20:49.374
